<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 234/68 1 of 27 February 1968 on the establishment of a common organisation of the market in live trees and other plants, bulbs, roots and the like, cut flowers and ornamental foliage, and in particular Article 4 thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 27. veebruari 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 234/68 elustaimede ja lillekasvatustoodete turu &uuml;hise korralduse kehtestamise kohta, (1) eriti selle artiklit 4, ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Section VI "Packaging and Presentation" of Annex I to Regulation (EEC) No 316/68 2 provides that a unit of presentation must consist of 5, 10 or a multiple of 10 pieces except for flowers normally sold singly or those normally sold by weight; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 316/68 (2) I lisa VI jaos "Pakend ja esitlus" n&auml;hakse ette, et esitlus&uuml;hik peab koosnema viiest, k&uuml;mnest v&otilde;i 10 kordsest t&uuml;kist, v&auml;lja arvatud harilikult &uuml;ksikult v&otilde;i kaalu j&auml;rgi m&uuml;&uuml;davate lillede puhul; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the application of this provision does not allow sellers of the products in question to satisfy in full the requirements of certain buyers who wish to have units of presentation at their disposal at fixed prices; whereas, therefore, the quality standards should be adjusted to take account of new trade requirements; </inglise>
<eesti> selle s&auml;tte kohaldamine ei v&otilde;imalda k&otilde;nealuste toodete m&uuml;&uuml;jatel t&auml;ita t&auml;ielikult teatavate ostjate n&otilde;udeid, kes soovivad esitlus&uuml;hikuid osta kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud hindadega; seep&auml;rast tuleks uute kaubandusn&otilde;uete arvessev&otilde;tmiseks kohandada kvaliteedistandardeid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the Opinion of the Management Committee for Live Plants; </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las elustaimede turu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The following text shall be substituted for the text of Section VI A of Annex I to Regulation (EEC) No 316/68: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 316/68 I lisa VI A jao tekst asendatakse j&auml;rgmisega: </eesti>
<inglise> "A unit of presentation (bunch, bouquet, box and the like) must consist of 5, 10 or a multiple of 10 pieces. </inglise>
<eesti> "Esitlus&uuml;hik (kobar, kimp, karp vms) peab koosnema viiest, k&uuml;mnest v&otilde;i 10 kordsest t&uuml;kist. </eesti>
<inglise> However this rule does not apply to: (a) flowers normally sold singly, </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevat eeskirja ei kohaldata: a) harilikult &uuml;ksikult m&uuml;&uuml;davate lillede suhtes, </eesti>
<inglise> (b) flowers normally sold by weight, </inglise>
<eesti> b) harilikult kaalu j&auml;rgi m&uuml;&uuml;davate lillede suhtes, </eesti>
<inglise> (c) flowers for which seller and buyer agree expressly to derogate from the provisions concerning the number of flowers in a unit of presentation. </inglise>
<eesti> c) lillede suhtes, mille puhul m&uuml;&uuml;ja ja ostja lepivad selges&otilde;naliselt kokku, et kaldutakse k&otilde;rvale n&otilde;uetest seoses lillede arvuga esitlus&uuml;hikus. </eesti>
<inglise> This derogation is admissible solely for transactions outside wholesale markets on condition that - the goods are the subject of a direct sale, based on a fixed selling-price per unit of presentation, at wholesale level to a retailer or a person acting on behalf of a retailer, </inglise>
<eesti> See erand on lubatav &uuml;ksnes hulgiturgude v&auml;listes tehingutes tingimusel, et: - kaupa m&uuml;&uuml;akse hulgim&uuml;&uuml;gitasandil otse jaem&uuml;&uuml;jale v&otilde;i jaem&uuml;&uuml;ja nimel tegutsevale isikule kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud m&uuml;&uuml;gihinnaga esitlus&uuml;hiku kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> - the goods are accompanied by a bill, delivery note or similar document showing the above-mentioned selling-price, </inglise>
<eesti> - kaubaga on kaasas arve, saateleht v&otilde;i samalaadne dokument, millel on n&auml;idatud eespool nimetatud m&uuml;&uuml;gihind, </eesti>
<inglise> - the unit of presentation is in the packaging required by the buyer for the ultimate purchaser. </inglise>
<eesti> - esitlus&uuml;hik on pakendis, mida ostja n&otilde;uab l&otilde;ppostja jaoks. </eesti>
<inglise> This packaging must be such as to permit identification of the goods. " </inglise>
<eesti> Selline pakend peab v&otilde;imaldama kaupa kindlaks teha." </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The following shall be added to Section VII of Annex I to Regulation (EEC) No 316/68: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 316/68 I lisa VII jaole lisatakse j&auml;rgmine: </eesti>
<inglise> "F Presentation </inglise>
<eesti> "F. Esitlusviis </eesti>
<inglise> If the number of flowers per unit of presentation does not correspond to the provisions of Section IV A, packages must be marked to show the exact composition of the units of presentation contained therein. " </inglise>
<eesti> Kui lillede arv esitlus&uuml;hiku kohta ei vasta IV jao A osa s&auml;tetele, tuleb pakenditele m&auml;rkida nendes sisalduvate esitlus&uuml;hikute t&auml;pne koostis." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. 1OJ No L 55, 2.3.1968, p. 1. 2OJ No L 71, 21.3.1968, p. 8. </inglise>
